{"tid":2336122,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想問我咁樣有冇得申請BNO?","createTime":"2020-12-22T11:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T19:51:10.000Z","uid":71001,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fda5476e313f21a2f8692d038f6518da66c7ae27","tid":2336122,"uid":71001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"我知我而家問有d遲<br />\n但我之前問左SAR果邊我到底有冇BNO身份<br />\n佢咁覆我：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnCCFxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnCCFxs.png&h=5c811958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;<span class=\"red\">An application for a BNO Passport was received, however, we do not have a passport number recorded for you.&rsquo;</span> 姐係咩意思 我究竟申唔申請到BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講少少背景資料先<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;合符以下條件基本上可以肯定你有過BNO身份：<br />\n<span class=\"red\">- 1997年7月1日前未滿11歲<br />\n- 身份證首次簽發日期為(06-97)或之前<br />\n- 香港出世而且出世紙寫有'Established'<br />\n- 曾經持有沒有相片的11歲以下人士香港兒童身份證&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n以上四樣我都中哂<br />\n我父母都有過BNO 但佢地應該無落到included child<br />\n佢地都話無幫我拎過BNO<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c89c790aa3b2a6965cafe61873fd10838c19f29","tid":2336122,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳下活動：<br />\n<br />\n快d入黎平安夜活動頻道!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2336042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2336042</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f583f2f38f21f55f92e3b894504da0056c31c382","tid":2336122,"u